'''André Blanc''' was a physiotherapist who became [[manager (association football)|manager]] of [[Olympique de Marseille]] for the 1942-43 season. He won the [[Coupe de France 1942-1943|Coupe de France]] in this season.<ref>{{cite book |editor=L'Équipe |title=Coupe de France : la folle épopée |author=Collectif |chapter= 1942-1943 - L'OM désormais sans rival |year=2007 |isbn=2-915535-62-0 |pages=431 |language=fr}}</ref>

